Okay, let's get things straight. Monsters Inc. was animated by Pixar in 2001 and distributed by Disney, but Disney did NOT own Pixar at the time, which means they did NOT force Pixar to change anything in Monsters Inc.. I hope it made things clear.

Oi! You missed a couple of characters and needed a little bit of spelling help, bro.

Zangief, Ryu, Ken and M. Bison, with the period, are from Street Fighter. That ghost is Clyde from Pac-Man, who also appears with Inky, Blinky, Pinky and Pac-Man. Eggman and Sonic are both from Sonic the Hedgehog. There's also Kano and Smoke from Mortal Kombat, a Zombie from the House of the Dead, the cast of Q-Bert, and Dig-Dug, just to name a few. The company is Disney, and it should have epicness. 

~MP1
